  "content": "<div class=\"content-main relative\">\n <h1 class=\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\">Bữa tiệc nhiếp ảnh quốc tế giữa l&ograve;ng Thủ đ&ocirc;</h1>\n <div class=\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [&amp;&gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n   <a href=\"/bao-giao-duc-thoi-dai-gd-td-p181.epi\" class=\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title=\"B&aacute;o Gi&aacute;o Dục &amp; Thời Đại\">\n    <figure class=\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style=\"width:36.25px;height:20px\" aria-label=\"Logo nh&agrave; xuất bản\">\n     <picture>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/a1aed5c10882e1dcb893.png\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/a1aed5c10882e1dcb893.png\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n      <img src=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/a1aed5c10882e1dcb893.png\" alt=\"B&aacute;o Gi&aacute;o Dục &amp; Thời Đại\" width=\"116\" height=\"64\" />\n     </picture>\n    </figure></a>\n   <span><button class=\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" title=\"Theo d&otilde;i &quot;GD&amp;TĐ&quot;\" aria-label=\"Button\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"></i></button></span>\n  </div>\n  <time datetime=\"2025-11-02T02:49:00.000Z\">16 giờ trước</time>\n  <a href=\"/photo-hanoi-t41412696.epi\" class=\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\">44\n   <!-- --> li&ecirc;n quan</a>\n  <a href=\"/bua-tiec-nhiep-anh-quoc-te-giua-long-thu-do-r53651213.epi\" class=\"origin item-origin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"></i><span>Gốc</span></a>\n  <i class=\"bm-icon inline-block bg-[url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/bm-icon-2.0.3.png)] bg-[length:100px_4250px] align-middle bg-[0_-723px] w-[23px] h-[23px]\"></i>\n </div>\n <h3 class=\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\">Photo Hanoi '25 đang mang đến một 'bữa tiệc thị gi&aacute;c' đa sắc, khẳng định vị thế của H&agrave; Nội như một trung t&acirc;m s&aacute;ng tạo nhiếp ảnh của ch&acirc;u &Aacute;.</h3>\n <div class=\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [&amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-[15px]\">\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Khởi động từ ng&agrave;y 1/11 tại <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/ha-noi-tag59.epi\">H&agrave; Nội</a>, Biennale Nhiếp ảnh quốc tế Photo Hanoi ’25 mở m&agrave;n cho một th&aacute;ng tr&agrave;n ngập sắc m&agrave;u nghệ thuật thị gi&aacute;c. Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; m&ugrave;a biennale thứ hai kể từ khi sự kiện được Viện Ph&aacute;p tại Việt Nam khởi xướng năm 2021, khẳng định vị thế H&agrave; Nội như một trung t&acirc;m s&aacute;ng tạo nhiếp ảnh của khu vực.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Sau hai m&ugrave;a 2021 v&agrave; 2023 với hơn 170.000 lượt kh&aacute;ch, 200 b&agrave;i b&aacute;o v&agrave; 5 triệu lượt tiếp cận mạng x&atilde; hội, Photo Hanoi đ&atilde; trở th&agrave;nh điểm hẹn uy t&iacute;n của giới nhiếp ảnh trong nước v&agrave; quốc tế.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Tiếp nối th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng đ&oacute;, Photo Hanoi ’25 đang quy tụ hơn 170 nghệ sĩ, gi&aacute;m tuyển v&agrave; chuy&ecirc;n gia từ 21 quốc gia, c&ugrave;ng 25 tổ chức chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n đồng h&agrave;nh.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Hơn 20 địa điểm tr&ecirc;n địa b&agrave;n Thủ đ&ocirc; được biến th&agrave;nh kh&ocirc;ng gian triển l&atilde;m mở, nơi c&ocirc;ng ch&uacute;ng được thưởng l&atilde;m 22 triển l&atilde;m c&aacute; nh&acirc;n v&agrave; nh&oacute;m ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n miễn ph&iacute;, c&ugrave;ng 29 sự kiện b&ecirc;n lề như hội thảo, workshop, art tour, chiếu phim, ra mắt s&aacute;ch v&agrave; portfolio review.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">C&aacute;c hoạt động hướng đến giao lưu chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n giữa giới nhiếp ảnh Việt Nam v&agrave; bạn b&egrave; quốc tế, gi&uacute;p nghệ sĩ trẻ học hỏi, mở rộng kết nối nghề nghiệp. Đ&acirc;y cũng l&agrave; dịp để người l&agrave;m ảnh nhận được phản hồi trực tiếp từ giới gi&aacute;m tuyển, đồng thời mở ra cơ hội hợp t&aacute;c xuy&ecirc;n bi&ecirc;n giới.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Kh&ocirc;ng chỉ l&agrave; s&acirc;n chơi chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n, Photo Hanoi ’25 c&ograve;n l&agrave; bữa tiệc thị gi&aacute;c đa sắc d&agrave;nh cho đ&ocirc;ng đảo kh&aacute;n giả. Chủ đề c&aacute;c triển l&atilde;m trải d&agrave;i từ k&yacute; ức lịch sử, cảnh quan đ&ocirc; thị đến c&aacute;c vấn đề to&agrave;n cầu như biến đổi kh&iacute; hậu, mối quan hệ con người – thi&ecirc;n nhi&ecirc;n.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Nhiều hoạt động trải nghiệm như chụp ảnh bằng m&aacute;y cổ, in ảnh thủ c&ocirc;ng, kỹ thuật bảng ướt thế kỷ 19 (wet plate), l&agrave;m s&aacute;ch ảnh thủ c&ocirc;ng… gi&uacute;p c&ocirc;ng ch&uacute;ng trực tiếp tham gia s&aacute;ng tạo, đưa nhiếp ảnh đến gần hơn với đời sống thường nhật.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">C&aacute;c triển l&atilde;m sẽ diễn ra tại những kh&ocirc;ng gian văn h&oacute;a quen thuộc như Viện Ph&aacute;p Việt Nam, Japan Foundation, Casa <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/italy-tag11058.epi\">Italia</a>, VCCA, Complex 01, Matca, Chau &amp; Co Gallery… c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c địa điểm c&ocirc;ng cộng như vườn hoa Di&ecirc;n Hồng, bờ hồ Ho&agrave;n Kiếm, tường Văn Miếu – Quốc Tử Gi&aacute;m hay mặt tiền Đại sứ qu&aacute;n Ph&aacute;p.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Photo Hanoi ’25 l&agrave; kết quả của sự chung tay từ hơn 10 đại sứ qu&aacute;n v&agrave; trung t&acirc;m văn h&oacute;a nước ngo&agrave;i tại Việt Nam, trong đ&oacute; c&oacute; Ph&aacute;p, &Yacute;, Đức, Nhật, Bỉ, <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/tuyen-tay-ban-nha-tag3613.epi\">T&acirc;y Ban Nha</a>, Anh, Thụy Sĩ… c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c tổ chức chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n quốc tế như Magnum Photo, Photo Phnom Penh Festival, La Station culturelle.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:415px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"415\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Kh&ocirc;ng chỉ l&agrave; sự kiện nghệ thuật, Photo Hanoi – Biennale nhiếp ảnh quốc tế c&ograve;n thể hiện cam kết mạnh mẽ của <a class=\"tag-link\" href=\"/tin-dia-phuong/ha-noi.epi\">H&agrave; Nội</a> trong việc triển khai c&aacute;c s&aacute;ng kiến của Mạng lưới Th&agrave;nh phố S&aacute;ng tạo UNESCO, g&oacute;p phần quảng b&aacute; h&igrave;nh ảnh, văn h&oacute;a, du lịch Thủ đ&ocirc;, th&uacute;c đẩy hợp t&aacute;c quốc tế v&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển c&ocirc;ng nghiệp văn h&oacute;a s&aacute;ng tạo.</p>\n  <p class=\"text body-author text-right\"><strong>Trần H&ograve;a</strong></p>\n </div>\n <div class=\"pswp\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"dialog\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  <div class=\"pswp__bg\"></div>\n  <div class=\"pswp__scroll-wrap\">\n   <div class=\"pswp__container\">\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__item\"></div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"pswp__ui pswp__ui--hidden\">\n    <div class=\"pswp__top-bar\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__counter\"></div>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--close\" title=\"Close (Esc)\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--share\" title=\"Share\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--fs\" title=\"Toggle fullscreen\"></button>\n     <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--zoom\" title=\"Zoom in/out\"></button>\n     <div class=\"pswp__preloader\">\n      <div class=\"pswp__preloader__icn\">\n       <div class=\"pswp__preloader__cut\">\n        <div class=\"pswp__preloader__donut\"></div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"pswp__share-modal pswp__share-modal--hidden pswp__single-tap\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__share-tooltip\"></div>\n    </div>\n    <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--left\" title=\"Previous (arrow left)\"></button>\n    <button type=\"button\" class=\"pswp__button pswp__button--arrow--right\" title=\"Next (arrow right)\"></button>\n    <div class=\"pswp__caption\">\n     <div class=\"pswp__caption__center\"></div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"content-social absolute top-[55px] w-[40px] h-full ml-[-75px]\">\n  <div class=\"content-social-container relative top-[unset] bottom-[unset] text-center w-[50px]\">\n   <button class=\"btn-social btn-facebook w-[40px] h-[40px] flex items-center justify-center text-[20px] mt-0 mb-[10px] rounded-[50%] bg-[#4e598f] hover:bg-[#